{"tid":1675223,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"屯門文宣手足反抗!!","createTime":"2019-10-25T17:09:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T07:31:34.000Z","uid":319891,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"3a6f5656d08028e242be024dec5821602c7f3a37","tid":1675223,"uid":319891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"啱啱經過屯門政署去安定既連儂隧道<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣比D廢老清晒</span></span></strong><br />\n係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清晒!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n成個隧道本身排得都唔比元朗國差 大家畫既Pepe比廢老填晒 我望到呢幕好激心 正當我諗住貼番D補一補嘅時間 發現有個藍衫廢老係度mon住 好L恐怖 <br />\n<br />\n我作為屯門手足既一份子決定動議<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;C One Paste Hun&quot;</span></strong></span>行動 簡稱「獅HUNT」 為連儂牆進行MAINTENANCE!! 有咩含意自己估<br />\n<br />\n現招各位屯門手足和議 每次2-3人小隊 進行1-2MB小型MAINTENANCE 用時間取勝<br />\n<br />\n因為好明顯近排連儂成為目標 為保手足安全 要帶多個睇水 獨行手足請自行選擇安全時間進行MAINTENANCE<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[black]<strong>We Are The Black Parade!</strong>[/black]</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"725e3ec082b20533b0c3ae5adc3ca73ae81e3e34","tid":1675223,"uid":761,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3a6f5656d08028e242be024dec5821602c7f3a37","tid":1675223,"uid":319891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"啱啱經過屯門政署去安定既連儂隧道<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">文宣比D廢老清晒</span></span></strong><br />\n係<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">清晒!!</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n成個隧道本身排得都唔比元朗國差 大家畫既Pepe比廢老填晒 我望到呢幕好激心 正當我諗住貼番D補一補嘅時間 發現有個藍衫廢老係度mon住 好L恐怖 <br />\n<br />\n我作為屯門手足既一份子決定動議<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">&quot;C One Paste Hun&q